Queries.name: Queries
Queries.description: Queries used in the ajax requests.

totalQuerySuccess.name: totalQuerySuccess
totalQuerySuccess.description: Callback for getStatistics. Creates pie chart with help of chart.js

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains total number of species

getPluralRank.name: getPluralRank
getPluralRank.description: Gets plural form of rank. Used in statistics message.

getArticle.name: getArticle
getArticle.description: Gets article used before rank. Used for greek translation.

articleRankSuccess.name: articleRankSuccess
articleRankSuccess.description: Callback for getSearchRank. Makes ajax request that gets name of previous rank member.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains counts of ranks

prevRankSuccess.name: prevRankSuccess
prevRankSuccess.description: Callback for articleRankSuccess. Gets most probable rank name from a list of possible rank names.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains possible ranks.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains wikipedia page url

getLanguageResources.name: getLanguageResources
getLanguageResources.description: Make arrays with static text in greek and english.

treeToGreek.name: treeToGreek
treeToGreek.description: Makes ajax request to convert tree branch to greek.

params.name: container
params.description: Container to be translated, usually tree branch

greekSuccess.name: greekSuccess
greekSuccess.description: Callback for treeToGreek. Puts the translated names in the DOM.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains a list with up to 50 names.

changeLanguage.name: changeLanguage
changeLanguage.description: Change language from greek to english and vice versa.

getGreekName.name: getGreekName
getGreekName.description: Ajax request to get greek translation of a name.

params.name: func
params.description: Variable to differentiate between call from stats or article

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax response that contains a greek name

showArticle.name: showArticle
showArticle.description: Saves the tree and loads article page

searchArticle.name: searchArticle
searchArticle.description: Gets value of searchbox and prepares query for article search.

saveTree.name: saveTree
saveTree.description: Saves the tree on index page

prettyLoadRank.name: prettyLoadRank
prettyLoadRank.description: Animation for pretty loading thumbnails in a rank

params.name: time
params.description: Duration of animation for loading of each element

checkUrl.name: checkUrl
checkUrl.description: Checks if dbpedia or dbpedia live is up and sets url accordingly

getImportantQuery.name: getImportantQuery
getImportantQuery.description: Query that gets members of rank species.

getOpenQuery.name: getOpenQuery
getOpenQuery.description: Query that gets members of next rank/tree branch.

getSearchRankQuery.name: getSearchRankQuery
getSearchRankQuery.description: Query that gets rank of search term.

getSummaryQuery.name: getSummaryQuery
getSummaryQuery.description: Query that gets summary of node from wikipedia.

returnGreekNameQuery.name: returnGreekNameQuery
returnGreekNameQuery.description: Query that gets greek name from an english name.

returnOneEnglishNameQuery.name: returnOneEnglishNameQuery
returnOneEnglishNameQuery.description: Query that gets english name from a greek name.

articleExistsQuery.name: articleExistsQuery
articleExistsQuery.description: Query that checks if a wikipedia article exists.

getprevRankNameQuery.name: getprevRankNameQuery
getprevRankNameQuery.description: Query that gets name of previous rank member.

params.name: rankIndex
params.description: Index of rank used to find rank from rankArray

getTotalQuery.name: getTotalQuery
getTotalQuery.description: Query that gets total number of species in rank.

getNextRank.name: getNextRank
getNextRank.description: Get next rank with help of rankArray.

getPrevRank.name: getPrevRank
getPrevRank.description: Get preious rank with help of rankArray.

ajaxError.name: ajaxError
ajaxError.description: Show error if something goes wrong with an ajax request.

$(document).on().name: $(document).on()
$(document).on().description:
Executed when somebody clicks on an open button.
Sets variables and calls function that creates next rank of tree.

summarySuccess.name: summarySuccess
summarySuccess.description:
Callback for ajax request in details click event. 
Adds the summary to the modal window.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax request response that contains node summary

getMembers.name: getMembers
getMembers.description: Makes ajax request to get important members of node.

params.name: page
params.description: The page from where the function was called, either index or article

membersSuccess.name: membersSuccess
membersSuccess.description:
Callback of getMembers ajax request called when the page is article.
Creates member thumbnails and loads them under article

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax request response that contains all members of rank species of a node

importantMembersSuccess.name: importantMembersSuccess
importantMembersSuccess.description:
Callback of getMembers ajax request called when the page is index.
Gets up to 8 most important members of rank species of a node.

params.name: _data
params.description: Ajax request response that contains all members of rank species of a node

executeOpenQuery.name: executeOpenQuery
executeOpenQuery.description: Makes ajax request that gets the next rank of the tree.

params.name: func
params.description: Variable that determines if function was called for a search or open

openSuccess.name: openSuccess
openSuccess.description: Callback of executeOpenQuery. Loads rank thumbnails in page.

params.name: _data
params.description: Response of ajax request query that contains members of rank

getSearchRank.name: getSearchRank
getSearchRank.description:
Callback from makeSearchTree. Gets members of all ranks up to the search term and calls
executeopenquery for each one.

params.name: selectedName
params.description: Used for search tree where node is selected automatically and not by the user

clearNextRanks.name: clearNextRanks
clearNextRanks.description: Clears next ranks of data to insert new nodes.

getThumbUrl.name: getThumbUrl
getThumbUrl.description: Returns shrinked thumbnail url or placeholder image if image doesn't exist.

startLoading.name: startLoading
startLoading.description: Adds loading span when something starts loading.

stopLoading.name: stopLoading
stopLoading.description: Removes loading span when something stops loading.

params.name: container
params.description: Container to remove loading span from

shrinkImg200.name: shrinkImg200
shrinkImg200.description: Returns image with width of 150 pixels.

shrinkImg300.name: shrinkImg300
shrinkImg300.description: Returns image with width of 300 pixels.

hideShowDivs.name: hideShowDivs
hideShowDivs.description: Toggle hiding and showing of divs.
